All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
Aliens
The Aliens class represents the alien entities in the game.
Border
The Border class represents a border element in the game, which is a polygonal shape used to define the boundaries of the game environment.
Bullets
The Bullets Class handles the bullets fired from all player and NPC objects.
Element
Abstract class for implementing the drawing of the objects needed for the project.
Obstacle
Obstacle class represents asteroid objects within the game environment.
PlayerShip
PlayerShip class handles the ship object that the player controls, where health points, movement and shooting mechanics are implemented here.
